ğŸ The Vulnerability:

ğŸ“Œ In config.sol of zkSync contracts, The BLOCK_PERIOD is set to 13 seconds in Config.sol.

ğŸ“ŒEthereum Since moving to Proof-of-Stake (PoS) after the Merge, block times on ethereum are fixed at 12 seconds per block (slots).

ğŸ“Œ This results in an incorrect calculation of PRIORITY_EXPIRATION which is used to determine when a transaction in the priority Queue should be considered expired.

ğŸ“Œ By using a block time of 13 sec, a txn in the Priority Queue expires 5.5 hours earlier than expected.

ğŸ’¡Recommended Mitigation Steps:
Change the block period to 12 seconds


